data.title: Leading Caterers of America
data.text:
DelightMore is Cincinnati’s premier event management company founded in 2004. DelightMore hosts hundreds of events per year in its own historic venues: Pinecroft at Crosley Mansion and The Transept in historic Over-the-Rhine, along with dozens of other venues and private homes. Known for its passion for quality and innovative approaches to menu preparation, DelightMore professionally trained staff prepares and serves all food on-site. From the first private tasting to the actual event, DelightMore is dedicated to make the event a memorable experience for the client. DelightMore is passionate about our community and donates its catering services and food/beverage to dozens of non-profits in Cincinnati annually including the American Heart Association, Cincinnati Ballet, Cincinnati Opera, Cincinnati Shakespeare Company, FC Cincinnati, among many others.
